# Cursor Rules for Spoteezer

## Command Execution
- Always use `just` commands when available instead of running commands directly
- For Python commands, use `uv run` instead of calling Python directly
- Prefer `just` commands from the root justfile or backend justfile over direct command execution
- Examples:
  - Use `just run` instead of `flask run`
  - Use `just test` instead of `pytest`
  - Use `just lint` instead of `ruff check`
  - Use `uv run <command>` for any Python tool execution
